Package cardseteditor

This package contains the objects for the card set editor.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardEditorCardSidePanel
    This class contains the panel to display and edit a side of a card.
    CardInfo
    This class contains the information about a card that is being edited.
    CardSetEditorDialog
    This class contains the dialog which allows the user to edit card sets.
    EditableCardSet
    This class contains the information which is to be written to a card set file..
    EditorDOM
    This class implements the editor document object model, and it provides routines for reading and writing card sets from and to files.
    EditorHelpDialog
    This class extends AbstractHelpDialog to implement a dialog in which the card set editor's help file is displayed.
